{"about_the_game":"In the 22nd Century people have settled the near-side of the moon, building massive mining operations for the benefit of Earth, while neglecting the needs of the Lunar people. Tensions with Earth are building, and hit a boiling-point when in 2134 a rogue nation suddenly seizes as much Lunar property as it can with deadly force. As an MI6 agent, you are sent to a mining station taken over by enemy forces in the Hadley-Apennine region. Eliminate the invaders, and frustrate their efforts! You're on your own, so be resourceful. Fight for King and planet!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Lunar Environment</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/HighresScreenshot00007.png?t=1699749500\" /><br>Feel how lunar gravity affects your gameplay. Achieve mad hops, send enemies flying, bounce around in the Lunar Pressurized Vehicle (LPV), or take off with a jetpack!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose Your Weapons</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/HighresScreenshotWeapons.png?t=1699749500\" /><br>Whether you are a gunslinger, heavy gunner, swordsman, or just like blowing things up, you will not be left out. Take on the enemy with a mixed arsenal of weapons that would otherwise weigh you down on Earth!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Freedom of Movement</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/HighresScreenshotBridge.png?t=1699749500\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Walk or run freely through the experience with smooth VR room-scale locomotion featuring 30 degree snap-turn for comfortable seated gameplay! Smooth player rotation is also supported as an option.<br></li><li>Standing or sitting, the game knows the difference at all times so you do not have to pause the game to change between the two modes.<br></li><li>No need to reach. Lightly hold the grip button and cast a laser to the objects you want to grab, then press fully to teleport them into your hand!</li></ul><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/extras/Nomad_Logo_512px.png?t=1699749500\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Skilled Operative","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/160414f774362cfa9877eecde85a188f7b0cd442.jpg"},{"name":"Elite Saboteur","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/2c4194fc3af6405afb979fce4db632aaafe7a405.jpg"},{"name":"Deadly Assassin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/80ad219049a2c63e47ce2af3ae8eed689ccdd188.jpg"},{"name":"War Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/c463e178798eb5f316f1d3e4c04fc9326a7ee298.jpg"},{"name":"His Majesty's Fixer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/bec89e55152c5a015ef2a458c01c9189030122f2.jpg"},{"name":"Hasta la vista, baby!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/cebf4f018460abbadc0dcfd132c58603934da8ba.jpg"},{"name":"Taking Flight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/250864621adae6069e75d99ef246cb873cd9e3c6.jpg"},{"name":"Hehehe YAAAAS!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/3dc46e61bda2fa30a7e2e26e460664249945681a.jpg"},{"name":"Lead Foot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/7fd8980013fc327556c45d1f9ce4b6a5fc295491.jpg"},{"name":"Demolition Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2386790/4ea5131591cd273d3ec8e963c57a01d61a341391.jpg"}],"total":12},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1699